<h1>Beowulf</h1>
<p>Transition to English. </p>
<ul>
	<li>written between 8th and 11th century. </li>
	<li>A "dark ages text." </li>
	<li>Anglo-saxon Literature (Old English, but much closer to German/Icelandic)  - 700 years. We have nothing in that era. </li>
	<li>1700-1936 - historical manuscript until he wrote an essay arguing that Beowulf was a piece of poetry, not just historical. They thought it was written by savages.</li>
	<li>Geat (Yowt). </li>
