</ul>
<p>mascunility, fear of death/conquest death, comeraderie, consequence. Beowulf sad that he has to go fight the dragon. He's an old man - better for him to lay down his life. All of our superheroes are not old. <br>Greed is dangerous. Don't look for things you don't deserve. Reward the people who help you. Superman could rob every bank, but he doesn't. The villain is the superhero who does rob the banks.<br>Beowulf has superpowers - walk under the ocean, rips arms off.</p>
