	<li>Non-canon. Canon - part of official story. It's a what if, has no consequences on the real story. It was originally intended to be non-canon. DC considered it accessible. Hard for new readers to understand because it has been told for 70 years. Superman was considered as a man out of time. This version could be appreciated by young people. Ended up doing really well so they made it canon. </li>
